{
  "stem": "15115.5",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 15.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The French army were coming through one place and the 7th-- 7th army, which was Eisenhower, coming in through the other place.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The train got stuck, couldn't move.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "No here, not there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's when we were liberated, right in the trains.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we got liberated in the trains.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We don't know yet.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, we see-- that was April 29, which is in the book.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We see the American tanks coming through, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we saw the star.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "That was the best day of our lives, which we saw the Americans coming in.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I met a Greek soldier into the tank.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You know, was in the tank.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So, you know, so I talked to him Greek.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And [INAUDIBLE] give us some food and so on.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But I was still in good shape.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "A lot of people were so weak, you know, from the agony and here or there that they were very, very-- we had a lot of dead bodies on the-- on the train, you know.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the German-- the Eisenhower came in.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he sees what he saw, that he couldn't believe his eyes, you know.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he brought in the Germans from the city to show what the Germans did to us.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And on the other side, the French came in from another section.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But the French just told us, come on, boys.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Let's go.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Let's kill a few Germans.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were coming with machine guns, going to German houses.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But there was nobody down there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "With the machine guns, grab whatever you can, because the Greek Jews spoke French, you know, most of them.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And you were, you know-- we started-- became buddies, you know, singing French songs and so on.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was sort of a nice gathering.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
